sequenceDiagram
    box Frontend
        participant Browser
        participant SPA
    end
    box rgb(220, 255, 220) Backend
        participant API
        participant Worker
    end
    Browser->>SPA: User action
    SPA->>API: Request
    API->>Worker: Enqueue job
    Worker-->>API: Done
    API-->>SPA: Response
    SPA-->>Browser: Update UI
